ibed with CYP450 3A4 inhibitors, particularly potent and moderate inhibitors (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/289073/', '', 'Alprostadil, Indomethacin, Ibuprofen, Ubidecarenone, Ivabradine, Adenosine, Regadenoson', '', 1767369485);
